1.0.name: wordpress/rbxgallery
1.0.description: RBX Gallery is a Post Image Gallery including RBX Slider plugin for WordPress. RBX Gallery now has a RBX Slider with many options. RBX Gallery provides gallery with thumbnails for each post.RBX Gallery Can be used by pasting a shortcode anywhere in the post or page with options width, thumbnail position,thumbnails size. RBX Gallery can be used to show multiple images for a product you are selling.You can the image view style in options like JQ Zoom or Light Box.
